A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a futuristic holographic spreadsheet floating in mid-air, with glowing neon grid cells in electric blue and magenta. The spreadsheet appears three-dimensional, with data cells rising at different heights like a cityscape. Streams of luminous data particles flow between cells, creating interconnected pathways. The scene is set in a dark environment with dramatic purple and teal ambient lighting, reflective surfaces below catching the glow. Small floating interface elements surround the main spreadsheet like orbiting satellites. The overall mood is innovative and cutting-edge, suggesting powerful technology being unveiled.
